2.2 Standard input
==================

The file name '-' means standard input:

$ cat FILE | hledger -f- print

   If reading non-journal data in this way, you'll need to add a file
format prefix, like:

$ echo 'i 2009/13/1 08:00:00' | hledger print -f timeclock:-


